Korean film shows in Russia 
&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Pyongyang, October 28 (KCNA) -- The DPRK Ambassador to Russia hosted film shows and receptions in Khabarovsk and Komsomolsk-On-Amur on Oct. 17 and 21.
 Screened at the film shows was Korean documentary film "The Great Leader Comrade Kim Jong Il's Visit to The Far Eastern Region of the Russian Federation". &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
 The governor of Khabarovsk territory, addressing the reception, said that Kim Jong Il's two visits to Khabarovsk in recent years were the greatest honor of the people of the territory. &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
 He went on: &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
 Kim Jong Il's current visit to the far eastern region shows well how favourably the Russia-Korea relations are developing. &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
 The meeting of the top leaders of the two countries is giving a strong impetus to the friendly and cooperative relations between the two governments and the two peoples. &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
 The bilateral relations will, no doubt, grow stronger in all fields including politics, the economy, science and technology, culture, and sports. &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
 The mayor of Komsomolsk-On-Amur in a speech, recalling the days of honor and excitement when Kim Jong Il visited the city, wished him good health and greater success in his work.

Probe into truth behind GIs' killings of schoolgirls urged 
&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Pyongyang, October 28 (KCNA) -- The all-people measure committee for schoolgirls Sin Hyo Sun and Sim Mi Son killed by U.S. armored car reportedly held a press conference in Seoul on Oct. 24, urging political camp to come out to probe the truth behind the GIs' killings.
 A press release was read out at the press conference. &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
 It said that all the people were demanding the probe into the truth behind the killings and punishment of those criminals but the U.S. troops, ignoring this, were holding only a deceptive trial at their military court. Even "acquittal" of the murderers was called for at the trial, an insult to the people, it noted. &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
 It strongly demanded that the national assembly form a fact-finding group and invoke the investigation right of the administration to do its utmost to stop the deceptive trial by the U.S. military authorities and make a definite probe into the truth. &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
 Those politicians who do not come out for the settlement of GIs' killings will be denounced and tried by the people as political swindlers seeking self-interest, it warned.

Independence in politics 
&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Pyongyang, October 28 (KCNA) -- The Juche idea elucidates an essence of independence in politics and indicates the way for realizing it.
 Maintaining independence in politics means defending the independence and sovereignty of one's country and the interests of one's people and pursuing politics by relying on one's people. &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
 Political independence is the most important criterion and lifeline of an independent and sovereign state. &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
 In order to realize the independence in all fields of the social life, it is imperative for the popular masses to realize the independence in the fields of the political life which takes a decisive and major position in the social life. &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
 It is also important for political independence to set up a people's government and build up strong political forces. &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
 Only when they set up the people's government, will they be able to solve all the problems in accordance with the interests of their people and the specific conditions of their country and ensure sovereignty in external relations. &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
 In order to guarantee political independence, it is also necessary to have one's own guiding thought and exercise complete sovereignty and equality in foreign relations. &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
 Political independence finds a graphic expression in working out and implementing all policies according to their own faith. &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
The policies, therefore, are specified by guiding thought. &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
 If one does not have one's own guiding thought, one cannot but follow or imitate others in working out and implementing the policies without principles and coherence. &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
 Only when each country fully exercises its sovereignty and equality, can it be called an independent and sovereign state which is able to provide its people with an independent and creative life. &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
 The principle of independence in politics is a scientific and revolutionary guiding principle that makes it possible for the people of each country to actually exercise the political sovereignty as the genuine masters of the state power, defend the national dignity and achieve the prosperity of the country.

Chongbong Information Center 
&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Pyongyang, October 28 (KCNA) -- The English-Korean translation system "Chongbong 1.0" came first in a national program competition and exhibition.
 It was developed recently by the Chongbong Information Center, one of the leading software bases of the Democratic People's Republic of Korea. &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
 The Chongbong Information Center has greatly contributed to the development of the country's program technique by developing a lot of effective programs. &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
 Typical of them are the Korean input system, Korean OCR Program and Korean-Japanese translation program. &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
 The programs developed by the center are exported to other countries including Russia, China and India. &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
 The center also offers the program order service in the way of dealing the language information with computer. &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
 Most of the centre's computer experts are young people in their 20s. &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
 The center is now concentrating on developing an automatic interpreting program.
